    genes.by.reactome.pathway

    genes.by.reactome.pathway.Rd

    A celltype pathway gene set from x <- readLines("c2.cp.reactome.v7.5.1.symbols.gmt") res <- strsplit(x, "\t") names(res) <- vapply(res, function(y) y[1], character(1)) genes.by.reactome.pathway <- lapply(res, "[", -c(1:2)) save(genes.by.reactome.pathway,file = "genes.by.reactome.pathway.RData")

    Usage

    data(genes.by.reactome.pathway)

    Format

    list

    Examples

    data(genes.by.reactome.pathway)
